+# Tidewatch5
+
+A tide prediction system.
+
+## Shipshape
+
+This project uses [Shipshape](https://github.com/dmytri/shipshape), a context-isolated spec-driven workflow for coding agents.
+
+### Rigging
+
+- **Stack**: JavaScript, Node.js 24.18.0, npm 12.0.1
+- **Implementation**: `src/`
+- **Specs**: `features/`
+- **Verification**: `features/support/`
+- **Assets**: `data/`
+
+### Workflow
+
+1. Captain writes specs in `features/`
+2. QM writes verification in `features/support/`
+3. Crew implements in `src/`
+4. Boatswain commits
+5. Shipwright inspects in harbour
+
+### Commands
+
+- Test: `npm test`
+- Focused: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- Discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run --format usage`
\ No newline at end of file
